 the rim) with a handle and two or more stabilizing prongs. A metal spring fixed around the edge of the rim rolls inward to fit inside the glass. The rim of the strainer does not need to touch the rim of the glass, as the spring inside filters out the ice. The Julep strainer is shaped like a bowl with a handle, and will fit tightly into a mixing glass or shaker when inserted at the proper angle. Liquid passes through holes or slits in the bowl.&lt;/p&gt;','https://img.thewhiskyexchange.com/900','equip_str1.jpg','The Whiskey Exchange','https://img.thewhiskyexchange.com/900/equip_str1.jpg',NULL,NULL,1,'Cocktail',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B0000DAQ93/ref=as_li_tl?ie=UTF8&camp=1789&creative=9325&creativeASIN=B0000DAQ93&linkCode=as2&tag=commonweal0ad-20&linkId=be74cd1e9121c887af9c8d7d3c9b651a'),(66,'Rums',1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(67,'Whiskey',1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(68,'Bulleit &amp;#39;95&amp;#39; Rye',1,'&lt;p&gt;A rich and spicy rye whiskey, with one of highest rye ratios (95%) we&#39;ve seen. Loaded with fruit and spice, it&#39;s a terrific rye for the price, and is just as tasty sipped neat as it is served in your favourite whiskey cocktail.&lt;/p&gt;',NULL,'https://img.thewhiskyexchange.com/900','brbon_bul5.jpg','The Whiskey Exchange','https://img.thewhiskyexchange.com/900/brbon_bul5.jpg',NULL,NULL,2,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Bulleit','https://www.bulleit.com/',NULL,NULL),(71,'Orange',6,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'Half','Slice',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(72,'Captain Morgan Spiced Gold Rum',1,'&lt;p&gt;Smooth and medium bodied, Captain Morgan&#39;s Spiced Gold gets its distinct richness and amber color from blending aged dark rum and spices.&lt;/p&gt;',NULL,'https://img.thewhiskyexchange.com/900','rum_cap2.jpg','The Whiskey Exchange','https://img.thewhiskyexchange.com/900/rum_cap2.jpg',NULL,NULL,2,NULL,NULL,4,NULL,NUL